&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welcome to Planet. We believe in using space to help life on Earth.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Planet designs, builds, and operates the largest constellation of imaging satellites in history. This constellation delivers an unprecedented dataset of empirical information via a revolutionary cloud-based platform to authoritative figures in commercial, environmental, and humanitarian sectors. We are both a space company and data company all rolled into one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customers and users across the globe use Planet&#39;s data to develop new technologies, drive revenue, power research, and solve our world’s toughest obstacles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we control every component of hardware design, manufacturing, data processing, and software engineering, our office is a truly inspiring mix of experts from a variety of domains.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a people-centric approach toward culture and community and we strive to iterate in a way that puts our team members first and prepares our company for growth. Join Planet and be a part of our mission to change the way people see the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Planet is a global company with employees working remotely world wide and joining us from offices in San Francisco, Washington DC, Germany, Austria, Slovenia, and The Netherlands.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Product Manager for Maritime Domain Awareness at Planet, you’ll be responsible for building scalable AI-enabled monitoring solutions that transform satellite imagery and multi-source data into actionable maritime insights. You will own end-to-end product strategy across analytics, APIs, user workflows, and operational customer requirements in support of defense and commercial maritime missions globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time, hybrid role which will require you to work from our Haarlem office 3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact You’ll Own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive the product vision for Maritime Domain Awareness, prioritizing capabilities like vessel detection features, upstream imagery requirements and change detection at the edge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop go-to-market strategies and pricing models for data tiers in coordination with Sales and Finance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High velocity development of near real-time analysis, collaborating with AI and machine learning teams, to optimize &quot;pixel-to-insight&quot; latency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather and prioritize requirements for near real time use cases, ensuring our products meet the needs of defense and commercial customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the product and market expert for Maritime Domain Awareness, representing Planet in technical forums and high-level customer briefings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with compliance and security teams to ensure all products and services adhere to export control laws, national security constraints, and data privacy standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of Product Management experience, specifically with a track record of launching complex, technical products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in a relevant field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of satellite systems and object detection analytics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to understand and represent the needs of users in mission-critical, near real time environments such as defense, intelligence, or disaster response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience balancing technical trade-offs and customer needs in complex product ecosystems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent interpersonal skills with the ability to work independently and as part of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication skills, with a knack for explaining complex technical trade-offs to both executive and engineering audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle multiple tasks simultaneously and prioritize appropriately.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes You Stand Out:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Maritime Domain Awareness in defense and commercial sectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of the current Maritime market across financial, insurance, and defense sectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
